-- Verizon's President Babbio to retire in first quarter
-- 
-- Mon Dec 11, 2006 6:49pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2006/12/11/us-verizon-babbio-idUSWNAS525920061211

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Verizon Communications Inc ( VZ.N ) said on Monday its Vice Chairman and President Lawrence Babbio has said he would retire at the end of the first quarter next year. 

 Verizon said it would announce transition plans in the coming weeks. Babbio has worked at Verizon and its predecessor companies for 41 years and is also on the company's board.